Name: Wolfram syndrome
Definition: A Wolfram syndrome that has_material_basis_in mutation in mtDNA.

Name: autosomal dominant Wolfram syndrome
Definition: A Wolfram syndrome that is characterized by congenital progressive hearing impairment

Name: Wolfram syndrome 1
Definition: An autosomal recessive disease that is characterized by diabetes mellitus

Name: Wolfram syndrome 2
Definition: An autosomal recessive neurodegenerative disorder characterized by diabetes mellitus
